@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - Blockchain Market Cap</PageTitle>

<div class="about-page">
    <div class="content-section">
        <h1>About Blockchain Market Cap</h1>

        <div class="info-card">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                Blockchain Market Cap provides real-time cryptocurrency market data to help users stay informed about
                the rapidly evolving blockchain and cryptocurrency space.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
            <h2>Data Sources</h2>
            <p>
                We utilize data from the CoinGecko API to provide accurate and up-to-date information on cryptocurrency
                prices, market capitalizations, trading volumes, and more.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://www.coingecko.com/en/api" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline btn-primary">
                    Learn more about CoinGecko API
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
            <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
            <p>
                This application is built using a hybrid architecture combining:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>ASP.NET Core with Blazor for server-side rendering</li>
                <li>Vue.js for dynamic client-side components</li>
                <li>TypeScript for type-safe JavaScript</li>
                <li>SCSS for organized and maintainable styling</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
            <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
            <p>
                The information provided on this site is for informational purposes only. Cryptocurrency investments are
                volatile and high-risk. Always conduct your own research before making any investment decisions.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>